{"tid":2283444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2019年11月12日: 警方就香港中文大學情況發表聲明 -- 呼籲示威者停止追擊","createTime":"2020-11-12T14:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T16:16:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46b86f8aafb396aa332fadd884fa4bd6a160f363","tid":2283444,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"警方就香港中文大學情況發表聲明<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  入夜後，香港中文大學（中大）的形勢持續緊張。為緩和目前形勢及希望以一個和平的方式解決問題，警方已和校方作出溝通，現正安排撤退以停止對峙情況，<strong><span class=\"red\">警方呼籲示威者停止追擊。警方的人群管理特別用途車輛在現場，有需要時將協助警方後撤。</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  同時，中大內的示威者亦不要向吐露港公路和港鐵路軌投擲物品，此舉會嚴重危害港鐵乘客和道路使用者的安全。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年11月12日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間22時10分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/12/P2019111200884.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F12%2FP2019111200884.htm&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BygfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=2c4f4bc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/12/P2019111200884.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6a1c654e5c67621de1702785147398703dbc6539","tid":2283444,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大大力"},{"pid":"ffc3210a105d859ac6b7879e9673587a74f01356","tid":2283444,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:33:51.000Z","msg":"之後就狂放tg"},{"pid":"ab6d4384c7a3b6ec4af331eadaba0136f793df81","tid":2283444,"uid":289708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffc3210a105d859ac6b7879e9673587a74f01356","tid":2283444,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"